Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.21,0:23:48.81,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,手を切るくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.99,0:23:53.58,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,痛ッ!證明したい マイ存在自体
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.38,0:23:56.93,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,永久ライン
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.18,0:24:01.67,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,囲い込まれても セーフティライン
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.16,0:24:05.15,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,「Wanna take you high ? 」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.42,0:24:10.11,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,揺れる銀河 君はスマイル
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.52,0:24:13.44,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,触れていたい
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.66,0:24:18.09,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,罰則なったとか 聞きたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.85,0:24:23.50,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,論にほだされ論理捨て
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.51,0:24:28.75,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,理性なきリスクゲームなど 申請
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.86,0:24:36.66,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,稀代の痛いのを以って 光彩
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.05,0:24:44.96,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,実際とアン実際とをミステイツク
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.28,0:24:53.00,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,一切の理解の向こうに So Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.50,0:24:57.16,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,So Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.52,0:25:01.12,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,So Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.71,0:25:09.52,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,So Fight!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-----TV-----
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.14,0:00:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从前 世上的诸多星辰混杂在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.67,0:00:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时人与神之间的界限还很模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.32,0:00:14.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而这 是个围绕一家之间的爱与重生的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.68,0:02:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 鞍马
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.22,0:02:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是就这样什么也没发生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.61,0:02:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琴会怎样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.93,0:02:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs35\fad(500,100)}欢迎回家 古都
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.53,0:02:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,病毒?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.05,0:03:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是妈妈啊 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.48,0:03:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.85,0:03:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:03.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琴?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.96,0:04:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琴?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 妈妈!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.13,0:04:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 我是琴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:13.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在找妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:16.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 我来接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.47,0:04:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是琴吧…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:44.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都想见到你 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是啊 琴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.42,0:05:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打——
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:32.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我有好多现在就想问的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.04,0:05:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过总之 我们先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.58,0:05:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在等着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古都…! 古都… 古都!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古都!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.62,0:06:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长得真漂亮啊 小公主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 老了不少啊 鞍马
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.23,0:06:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是那么美丽 古都
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.22,0:06:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.76,0:06:24.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你长大啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能一个人睡了吗 明惠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.94,0:06:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.84,0:06:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都有这么多孩子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.60,0:06:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:45.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥他们让你乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.52,0:06:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不可以原谅他们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能见到你真的很开心 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来——
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀唉呀 真是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.20,0:07:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里变化真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:29.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是古都大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.29,0:07:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古都大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古都大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,值得庆幸 值得庆幸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是三人议会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真显眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.56,0:07:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们按照约定 齐心合力保护好镜都了呐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.51,0:08:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们三个 都很厉害呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.45,0:08:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 咱们去山上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.18,0:08:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我准备为妈妈开一次茶会哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八濑负责山上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.04,0:08:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 明惠负责偷懒~哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你负责什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.23,0:08:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是照顾小孩子就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.07,0:08:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在说我们么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真过分——
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:25.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能有谁啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实很喜欢的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不在你要哭的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.24,0:08:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没出息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.71,0:08:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我闭嘴 你们这群笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.33,0:08:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是鞍马想出来的么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.51,0:08:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是那么厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:43.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想看更多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.78,0:08:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.25,0:08:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,显示屏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:52.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,显示屏?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按下这里颜色就会变么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.63,0:08:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好不要乱碰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:08:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.92,0:09:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是变色的道具哟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位就是三人议会的母亲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.29,0:09:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她走的时候 你还没来么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.12,0:09:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是我的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.88,0:09:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都不像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有这种事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.09,0:09:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超像的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 差不多就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:24.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.93,0:09:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这突然间 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.82,0:09:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然好像!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:33.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都做了些什么啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.82,0:09:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.69,0:09:42.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用来我家啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.24,0:09:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 有什么关系嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:45.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么可展示的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.74,0:09:47.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我想看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄得很漂亮嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.97,0:09:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你喜欢做饭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般般…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.49,0:09:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是那么勤快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:10:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是我和阿吽的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:03.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过出门前好好收拾一番的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 请品尝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.09,0:10:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.58,0:10:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.94,0:10:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和以前妈妈喝的是一样味道的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真令人怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真亏你能留这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为都是和妈妈的珍贵的回忆嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以丢掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.40,0:10:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能回来 我真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.27,0:10:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八濑…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然离开 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.36,0:10:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.32,0:10:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系啦 古都
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.35,0:11:04.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.98,0:11:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 妈妈差不多要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:13.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.38,0:11:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:15.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好不容易才回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正也看到大家精神满满的样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.19,0:11:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然说好了要一起回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我随随便便就抢先了 会惹他生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.26,0:11:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸他 过些时候也会随随便便就回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八濑…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:39.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你说要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.77,0:11:40.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但要怎么回去?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不干哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事我可不再做了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 你到底是怎么来到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是商业秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.07,0:11:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明就回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:11:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古都
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要——
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:06.60,note-white,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}注：日语中的「異」与「琴」和「古都」同音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起啊 让你那么慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.98,0:12:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.40,0:13:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长大了呀 琴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一次见你的时候 你还是个小婴儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是婴儿的时候见过妈妈吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.03,0:13:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时你才这么大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.96,0:13:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还曾经一起去过那个地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.30,0:13:24.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.24,0:13:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一点都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.92,0:13:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸什么都没告诉你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.35,0:13:36.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像他不太想说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:39.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该说 他总是像这样——
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摆出一种「我不用说你也明白吧」的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真像他的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来他以前就是这个样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个样子我怎么可能懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.17,0:14:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头发跟你爸爸一样柔顺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.18,0:14:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.40,0:14:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:19.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有眼睛的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对喔 一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.03,0:14:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也跟妈妈一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.84,0:14:57.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.24,0:15:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 你真的要回去那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.18,0:15:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的 那里是神社的圣地对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.38,0:15:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会在那种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琴…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师还有神社里的各位 什么都不告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.99,0:15:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我想知道呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.77,0:15:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于我自己 关于爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.98,0:15:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有关于妈妈 我都想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚开始看到你的时候 我还以为是上人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.13,0:15:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为他遵守约定 来接我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:52.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以为虽然过去了许多时间 他还是来兑现诺言了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 果然事情没有那么顺利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.96,0:16:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琴 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:10.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能拯救那个被囚禁在梦境中的可怜人?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.79,0:16:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您妹妹砸开的洞 已经闭合了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个触媒照这情况 也会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.44,0:16:32.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.64,0:16:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总感觉不太对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么她能这么干脆地说出「要回去」这话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.47,0:16:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 妈妈差不多要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.63,0:17:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天你不是住在那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.10,0:17:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次进来这个房间 还真是什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.91,0:17:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你女朋友也不来这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不是我女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:57.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我配不上她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.15,0:18:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一上来就说「我怎样怎样」这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整天就会说这种话 不累?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.79,0:18:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.92,0:18:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明惠你真是好啊 有个可以玩世不恭的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羡慕死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.09,0:18:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不也有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.02,0:18:30.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.97,0:18:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…只有未来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.70,0:18:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不向未来前进 我就只会一直一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.05,0:18:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.35,0:19:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不说我怎么知道你在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…大家都只会拜托我做事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.23,0:19:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琴…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明也有好多想问想拜托别人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 大家却什么都不告诉我!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.32,0:19:27.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点啊 琴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.75,0:19:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不干了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.03,0:19:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有好多烦恼的呀!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.93,0:19:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是因为你很特别
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.88,0:20:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是没办法的事 琴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.32,0:20:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老…师?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关键是习惯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.12,0:20:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.51,0:20:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.77,0:20:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又哭了啊 胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.10,0:20:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是长不大的小孩子 小不点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.72,0:20:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的泪水也是好久不见了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 还有猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:39.54,note-white,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}注：老师身边的黑白两只东西一只叫ね一只叫こ，\N类似于一只叫「猫」一只叫「咪」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.77,0:20:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在这里干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.43,0:20:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里可是镜都啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.36,0:20:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.06,0:21:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.55,0:21:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是上人…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.78,0:21:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,药师丸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.26,0:21:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 现在的你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.81,0:21:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是明惠上人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.34,0:21:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 你是怎么来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.40,0:21:34.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为你们太淘气了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.13,0:21:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜们闹过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.45,0:21:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都要忙得不可开交了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.68,0:21:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做的事可不得了啊 假小子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.56,0:22:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦的后续…为什么现在出现?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.47,0:22:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原因只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.04,0:22:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.70,0:22:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神社所惧怕 想要隔离的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.80,0:22:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.95,0:22:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎么来到镜都的 琴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.91,0:22:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么来?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.10,0:22:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了个入口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.50,0:23:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为找不到入口嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.59,0:23:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就用璞玉强行介入了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.51,0:23:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师也做过啊 用你的神刀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.69,0:23:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从你的样子来看 应该是毫无疑问的了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.00,0:23:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 什么都没变
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.86,0:23:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灾厄之事 全是爸爸带来的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.28,0:23:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是经常说嘛「可爱的妹妹」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.51,0:23:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也找到妈妈了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.73,0:23:39.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒吧 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.58,0:25:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镜都街道开始全面崩塌?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.09,0:25:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.97,0:25:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事根本不好笑啊 没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.80,0:25:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过宫司也来了 总有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.72,0:25:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切的原因是…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.85,0:25:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.45,0:25:33.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 那边和这边争执不下
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.77,0:25:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌 根本没听说会这样啊老师
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.19,0:25:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
